quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,91,"And when it is said to them (the Jews), "
  2,92,"And indeed Mûsâ (Moses) came to you with clear proofs, yet you worshipped the calf after he left, and you were Zâlimûn (polytheists and wrongdoers)."
  2,93,"And (remember) when We took your covenant and We raised above you the Mount (saying), "
  3,31,"Say (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم to mankind): "
  3,32,"Say (O Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم): ",1:[{3:32} See the footnote of {3:85}]
  3,33,"Allâh chose Adam, Nûh (Noah), the family of Ibrâhîm (Abraham) and the family of ‘Imrân above the ‘Âlamîn (mankind and jinn) (of their times)."